  "3256610": {
    "name": "Bubble Balance Bonanza",
    "steam_appid": 3256610,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256610/extras/ceecf4f80f659543b8b85313d46b8d37.webp?t=1762785835\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roll, bump, jump, and crash your way through many unique levels in this fast-paced, marble style, physics-driven platformer. With unpredictable environments, cute characters to meet and interact with and crazy obstacles to overcome, you'll need both skill and strategy to keep your balance and complete the journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Are you ready for the bonanza?</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256610/extras/29926d378332401a8af5383186b69cd6.poster.avif?t=1762785835\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256610/extras/29926d378332401a8af5383186b69cd6.webm?t=1762785835\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256610/extras/29926d378332401a8af5383186b69cd6.mp4?t=1762785835\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256610/extras/a5dad7da127c8cb5a9bbd939d502f993.webp?t=1762785835\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Protected by a bubble, you'll embark on a wild adventure through an unknown and treacherous world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With over 30 levels to explore and complete, you'll meet many other creatures, animals and friends! <i>Bubble Balance Bonanza</i> features a dynamic world map where you’ll roll around to select new levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256610/extras/0a7321e69ae803c246a75506106c583a.poster.avif?t=1762785835\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256610/extras/0a7321e69ae803c246a75506106c583a.webm?t=1762785835\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256610/extras/0a7321e69ae803c246a75506106c583a.mp4?t=1762785835\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256610/extras/f72f5c0b808b1da474b89fa8a5e4d2df.webp?t=1762785835\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Bubble Balance Bonanza</i> puts you in control of a young and determined T-Rex tasked with an important mission: to venture into the wild unknown and recover the precious eggs of its unborn siblings. Guided by a strong sense of duty, this brave T-Rex must navigate treacherous terrain, facing all manner of challenges and dangers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256610/extras/fe08a4c7e5b9241097d6fc169ace9e1a.poster.avif?t=1762785835\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256610/extras/fe08a4c7e5b9241097d6fc169ace9e1a.webm?t=1762785835\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256610/extras/fe08a4c7e5b9241097d6fc169ace9e1a.mp4?t=1762785835\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256610/extras/b6ad11178f296840b267948260cc50a1.webp?t=1762785835\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enclosed in a protective bubble, your journey will take you through a variety of unpredictable environments, from lush forests to perilous cliffs. The bubble isn’t just for protection—it becomes your primary tool for navigating this hazardous world. You'll need to master the physics of rolling, bouncing, and crashing as you overcome obstacles, avoid enemies, and solve puzzles to rescue the fragile eggs scattered across the land.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's a race against time and the elements in a quest for survival. Will you have the skill and bravery to bring your siblings safely home?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256610/extras/96197f0442c6034e4c72479aa7e08fef.poster.avif?t=1762785835\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256610/extras/96197f0442c6034e4c72479aa7e08fef.webm?t=1762785835\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256610/extras/96197f0442c6034e4c72479aa7e08fef.mp4?t=1762785835\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
